{"tid":2514573,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"專挑健身男！ 捷運站外尾隨「噴不明液體」","createTime":"2021-05-03T10:42:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T11:50:27.000Z","uid":3189,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"215da5707d586ee1818d29b4c142090c593a6656","tid":2514573,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:42:33.000Z","msg":"北市士林捷運站，竟然出現尾隨攻擊怪男！26日早上九點多，王先生才剛出站，就發現有陌生男子在尾隨他，甚至還假裝製造，不經意的「肢體接觸」，當下覺得不舒服，就馬上出聲制止，沒想到對方，竟惱羞成怒，拿出預藏的「罐裝噴霧」噴灑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NRixc0lzLXA_3hXORLc9Lw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUzOS43NzM1ODQ5MDU2NjA0O2NmPXdlYnA-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/.DNr7qD2ib41df2ZYxb.vw--~B/aD01OTY7dz0xMDYwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/news_tvbs_com_tw_938/add1dc13486e3f865c10ca6fa2596fe7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FNRixc0lzLXA_3hXORLc9Lw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUzOS43NzM1ODQ5MDU2NjA0O2NmPXdlYnA-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F.DNr7qD2ib41df2ZYxb.vw--~B%2FaD01OTY7dz0xMDYwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fnews_tvbs_com_tw_938%2Fadd1dc13486e3f865c10ca6fa2596fe7&h=37c1e04c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n身材壯碩的男子，緩緩走出捷運站，頭卻頻頻往後張望，像在找些什麼，這時一名背心平頭男，慢慢跟了上去，看似和一般乘客，沒什麼兩樣，但他其實早有鎖定目標，沿途尾隨這名壯碩男性，甚至還製造，不經意的「肢體接觸」。<br />\n<br />\n被害人王先生：「通常我可能就會走路，他(嫌犯)就會故意從後面跟上來，然後稍微這樣，去碰你一下，然後對這行為，我就很反感。」<br />\n<br />\n受不了被陌生人觸碰，大聲指責，沒想到換來的，竟是更激烈的攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/6LBGgvMWERxWbv4xHRBh.w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/news_tvbs_com_tw_938/f95908dbdf7eac8ae627b73654861cf9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F6LBGgvMWERxWbv4xHRBh.w--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtjZj13ZWJw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fnews_tvbs_com_tw_938%2Ff95908dbdf7eac8ae627b73654861cf9&h=051467d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這回又被人指控尾隨騷擾，甚至還出手攻擊，不管目的是什麼，用這種方式，已經嚴重逾越了界線。<br />\n<br />\n被害人王先生：「我就轉頭問他(嫌犯)說，你要幹嘛，他就拿東西噴我，我那時候就趕快手遮住眼睛這樣，不知道那是什麼。」<br />\n<br />\n隨機被人，噴灑不明液體，王先生根本來不及防備，第一時間，只好跑進附近銀行，請保全幫忙，初步清洗後想報警，嫌犯卻早就跑了，事後仔細回想才發現，原來這人，就是兩年前的那個他。<br />\n<br />\n類似的長背心裝扮、配黑長褲，只差在髮型比較長，王先生說，兩年前，這名嫌犯，就已經在士林捷運站附近徘徊，年約35歲、身高大概170公分，每每現身，都是背心配這只側背包，在捷運站附近找尋目標，還特別偏好，有健身、身材壯碩的男性。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pugk9H6EJ_V_NlkSg7z_fg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/news_tvbs_com_tw_938/60c4cb8950d279a0d36d19bdb51145ba\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fpugk9H6EJ_V_NlkSg7z_fg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtjZj13ZWJw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fnews_tvbs_com_tw_938%2F60c4cb8950d279a0d36d19bdb51145ba&h=cb843003&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《TVBS》提醒您勇敢說不：<br />\n<br />\n◎尊重身體自主權，遇到性騷擾勇於制止、勇敢說不，請撥打113、110<br />\n<br />\n◎現代婦女基金會 性侵害防治服務專線02-7728-5098分機7<br />\n<br />\n◎婦女救援基金會 02-2555-8595<br />\n<br />\n性侵防範要點：<br />\n<br />\n◎察覺對方有性侵意圖時，應冷靜設法離開現場，並立即求救；若遭限制行動，勿過<br />\n<br />\n度刺激對方，千萬不要抵死反抗。<br />\n<br />\n◎相信直覺！拒絕不舒服或不喜歡的肢體接觸。<br />\n<br />\n◎睡覺或盥洗時，門窗要上鎖。<br />\n<br />\n◎避免與有酒醉、吸毒、有暴力傾向或性犯罪前科的人獨處。<br />\n<br />\n◎當對方出現你認為不妥的言行時，應立刻離開或制止。<br />\n<br />\n◎如遭性侵，應立即報警與求助信任的人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbXoAEGrb2r7AwEESrbRankfSdc9Xw6XJbd5QQQjW5dAf?filename=pdTjHof.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpdTjHof.gif&h=8d7c39cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be63a00e1122eb809ba1f5c264277ec773edbe6d","tid":2514573,"uid":27064,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:44:12.000Z","msg":"Cam man做到嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad5a4813ac77c4d841416e2cba2ad01f3e72781c","tid":2514573,"uid":89131,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:45:34.000Z","msg":"著到咁都係搏俾人非禮"},{"pid":"2868225eea77b6d70e8